Ferdium is a free and open-source application that allows you to manage multiple messaging, social media, and productivity apps in a single interface. It's a fork of Franz and is designed to help users organize and centralize their communication tools. Ferdium supports a wide range of services, including WhatsApp, Slack, Gmail, Twitter, and many others, by running each service in a tab within the app. It also offers additional features like workspace management, session management, and enhanced privacy controls.
